race.description: Betdeluxe Con Sciacca Capalaba Cup Ht
race.comment: SERIAL STICKER (6) is progressing well with another good run last time, placing (18.89) from Box 2 at Healesville. Has a very good strike-rate from this draw, with two wins from four starts. Rates highly and will give a great sight. VALIDATE (7) was strongly supported last start when a short priced favourite and duly saluted winning by 4.5 lengths at Q Lakeside in a handy 25.05. Draws out wide but in form and has the ability. Must be included in calculations. ALSTON (2) is progressing well with another good run last time, placing (25.12) last time out at Shepparton. Didn't win last time but still ran one of the quickest times on the card. Leading player again. LEVI DESIGN (1) was strongly supported last start but missed the frame when sixth (18.02), beaten 5 lengths. The form from his last run stacks up well.

runners.name: Alston
